view.name: Births By Age of Mother, 1960-2013
view.description: This dataset is for California live births by age of mother, for years 1960-2013. The live birth counts per age bracket represent the live births to California resident mothers, regardless of the place of birth occurrence. The live birth count includes live births to California resident mothers giving birth outside of California.  Live births to non-California resident mothers who gave birth inside California are not included in the dataset.
